<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> karṇnāṭāṁdrakali<unclear>ṁ</unclear>ggakuṁttalapatīnnirjjitya yassaṁyugē svādhīnāmmahatīmmahī<unclear>manubhavansāṁ</unclear>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mrājyacihnai<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> sthitaḥ [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1*] yēna śrīpuruṣōttamasya nilayē śrīparvatāgrēpi tatkuṁbhau hēmamayau vijitya ca
<lb n="4"/>bhuvāṁ staṁbhāviva sthāpitau <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> prāsādēna yutaṁ suvarṇnavimalaṁ bhīmēśvarasyōcitaṁ yēnādāyi suva
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rṇnapātramamitaṁ tasmaibhavāyādarāt [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] tasya śrīgoṁkkabhūpasya mahiṣī prōlamāṁbikā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> rāja
<lb n="6" break="no"/>tē rā<unclear>jya</unclear>lakṣmīva sarvvāvayavasuṁdarī [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 3*] murajita Iva lakṣmīḥ pārvvatīvēṁddumaulērddinakṛta Iva yōṣādē
<lb n="7" break="no"/>vabharttuśśacīva<supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>bhuvi vilasati dēvī prōlamāṁbā sa<unclear>tī sā</unclear>dvijakulajaladhīṁdōgo<supplied reason="omitted">9</supplied>ṁkkabhūpālakasya [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 4*] Ā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>sīddhanapurigrāmē śrīmāneṟiyanaprabhuḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> patnī guṇavatī tasya yeṟiyāsānīti viśrutā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">5</supplied>tābhyāmabhūnma 
<lb n="9" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> lāvaṇyasaṁppannā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vilāsinī tasyāssarvvaguṇōpētā sudatī cāru <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> hitē<note n="398-1">The rest of the inscription is completely damaged.</note>
